<a href="/my_book" class="back-link">← My Book</a>
<h1>Import Recipe from URL</h1>
<p style="color:var(--text-secondary); margin-bottom:var(--space-xl);">Paste the URL of a recipe blog or cooking site. We'll extract the recipe automatically using structured data, and fall back to AI if needed.</p>

<div class="card" style="max-width:540px;">
  <form action="/recipes/import" method="post">
    <%= hidden_field_tag :authenticity_token, form_authenticity_token %>
    <div class="form-group">
      <label class="form-label">Recipe URL</label>
      <input type="url" name="url" required class="form-input" placeholder="https://…">
    </div>
    <div class="form-actions">
      <button type="submit" class="btn btn--primary">Import Recipe</button>
    </div>
  </form>
</div>

<p class="text-sm mt-md">Or <a href="/recipes/new">create a recipe manually</a>.</p>
